<subSubSection id="C3326533FFA8FFE9E8BB232CFDCBFE6C" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="368" pageId="2" pageNumber="365" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B9736B8FFA8FFEEE8BB232CFCDFFE69" blockId="2.[166,1225,289,412]" pageId="2" pageNumber="365">
D e s c r i p t i o n. Male. Total length 2.75 (variations 2.5‒2.85). Carapace 1.36 long, 1.0 wide with distinct pattern. Eye sizes and interdistances: AME 0.10, ALE = PLE 0.04, AME- AME 0.03, PME 0.05, PME-PME 0.10. Clypeus 0.14. Legs I‒II thinner than III‒IV, middle part of femur I 
<quantity id="4CD09B5DFFA8FFEEE93A238CFE54FE69" box="[346,426,385,412]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.556" pageId="2" pageNumber="365" unit="in" value="0.14">0.14 in</quantity>
diameter and femur IV — 0.24.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9736B8FFA8FFEEE8BB20BBFB36FD24" blockId="2.[166,1224,694,753]" box="[219,1224,694,721]" pageId="2" pageNumber="365">
