<figureCitation id="13132A3DFFA8FFEEEA6720BBFDB3FD24" box="[519,589,694,721]" captionStart="Figs 1‒7" captionStartId="1.[170,209,1766,1788]" captionTargetBox="[235,1164,612,1730]" captionTargetId="figure-137@1.[235,1164,612,1730]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="Figs 1‒7. Habitus and male palp of Argistes velox: 1–2 — female habitus, lateral and dorsal; 3 — male habitus, lateral; 4‒5 — male palp, retro- and prolateral; 6‒7 — prosoma frontal in female and male. Scale = 0.2 mm if not otherwise indicated." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449352" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449352/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="365">figs 3</figureCitation>
, 
